        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: PSD fractions were prepared from rat forebrains and cerebellums and subjected to mass spectrometry.\n\n13/11/2017 Pim\n- Protein listed as \"poly(rC) binding protein\" accession NP_001013241.1\n- Proteins are compared as ratio's between forebrain and cerebellum abundance implying expression in both brain area's.. Experimental description: Subspecies, age or other: not specified." ;
